snippet.title: Laser Dance - Official Developer Teaser Trailer | Upload VR Showcase
snippet.description: Get a peek at Laser Dance in this new teaser, and join the developer to learn more about this upcoming mixed-reality game that turns your living room into a laser obstacle course. Laser Dance is available to wishlist now on the Meta Quest Store.
